  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bulgarian as a second language</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project raises funds for the development of a methodology for teaching Bulgarian to students in primary school (grades 1-4) who are not yet fluent in the language. There is an urgent need for such a methodology, which will provide an equal start at school for children whose mother tongue is different from Bulgarian. At the moment TFB teachers are working with 1823 students who are in such situation and would benefit from this project, with more likely to be reached in the coming year.</narrative>
  </description>
